---
import { C, FONT } from "../infographicTokens";
---

<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 720 320" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
  <title>Tonnage and airflow rules</title>
  <desc>One ton equals 12,000 BTU per hour, a system needs about 400 CFM per ton, and CFM equals velocity times duct area.</desc>

  <text x="360" y="32" text-anchor="middle" fill={C.dark} font-family={FONT} font-size="16" font-weight="700">Tonnage &amp; airflow rules</text>

  <!-- Tonnage -->
  <rect x="60" y="54" width="600" height="62" rx="10" fill={C.primaryLight} stroke={C.primary} stroke-width="1.5" />
  <text x="84" y="80" fill={C.primary} font-family={FONT} font-size="11" font-weight="700">CAPACITY</text>
  <text x="360" y="92" text-anchor="middle" fill={C.dark} font-family={FONT} font-size="18" font-weight="800">1 ton = 12,000 BTU/hr&#160;&#160;&#8594;&#160;&#160;tons = BTU/hr &#247; 12,000</text>

  <!-- 400 CFM/ton -->
  <rect x="60" y="128" width="600" height="62" rx="10" fill={C.blueLight} stroke={C.blue} stroke-width="1.5" />
  <text x="84" y="154" fill={C.blue} font-family={FONT} font-size="11" font-weight="700">RULE OF THUMB</text>
  <text x="360" y="166" text-anchor="middle" fill={C.dark} font-family={FONT} font-size="18" font-weight="800">&#8776; 400 CFM per ton&#160;&#160;(350&#8211;450 range)</text>

  <!-- Velocity x area -->
  <rect x="60" y="202" width="600" height="62" rx="10" fill={C.panelBg} stroke={C.border} stroke-width="1.5" />
  <text x="84" y="228" fill={C.dark} font-family={FONT} font-size="11" font-weight="700">DUCT VELOCITY</text>
  <text x="360" y="240" text-anchor="middle" fill={C.dark} font-family={FONT} font-size="18" font-weight="800">CFM = velocity (fpm) &#215; area (ft&#178;)</text>

  <text x="360" y="294" text-anchor="middle" fill={C.muted} font-family={FONT} font-size="11">A 3-ton system moves &#8776; 1,200 CFM. At 600 fpm that needs &#8776; 2.0 ft&#178; of total duct area.</text>
</svg>
